    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在不远的未来，一种可怕的病毒影响了人类，将大部分人变成了僵尸。你作为最后的幸存者之一，必须奋力杀向一切开始的地方，结束这一切。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您喜欢塔防类游戏，但有时又缺乏动力，那么您来对地方了。我们的团队为您提供了这一类型的新玩法，我们试图在其中添加更多的动作性、动态性和非线性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>塔楼防御</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>各种具有不同功能的建筑将让您能够为自己定制游戏。在我们的游戏中，您已经放弃了预设的最佳建筑地点，您的任何冒险都可以在这里进行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>武器和定制</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>成功闯关后，别忘了获得独特的角色皮肤或武器，从而脱颖而出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>独特的地点和老板</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>7 个完全不同的地点以及独特的敌人和 BOSS 绝对不会让你感到无聊，而困难模式则会让你面临真正的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽可能多地建造、适应和享受乐趣--这是我们游戏的座右铭。</p>",
